From 5c8840558c1c34879e53a29c83a17839c14c18a3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 19 May 2026 00:26:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] M408-M409: Extract histogram-only first pass, factor
 finalize_pass, LOC+SP 13B bridge, restructure dispatch loop

Following CCCL f984c90 (Extract first histogram-only pass in DeviceTopK
into its own kernel), this commit applies the same kernel extraction
and dispatch restructuring discipline to Neuron_SP AutoSP:

=== M408: Kernel extraction + LOC bridge ===

sp_histogram.py:
  - Extract invoke_histogram_only() as standalone pass-0 kernel
    (mirrors AgentTopK::invoke_histogram_only)
  - Add invoke_filter_and_histogram() for pass>=1 with candidate masking
  - Factor finalize_pass() as reusable method taking counter_update_fn
    callable (mirrors AgentTopK::finalize_pass<CounterUpdateFn>)
  - Add PassCounter dataclass for cross-pass state tracking
  - Add run_filter_and_histogram_pass() top-level dispatch

double_buffer_a2a.py:
  - Align DoubleBuffer.swap() with CCCL key_bufs.selector ^= 1 pattern
  - Add _swap_count tracking and swap_count() accessor

sp_dp_registry.py:
  - Add LOC state: loc_enabled, loc_sp_group_ids in _MESH_META
  - Add is_loc_enabled(), enable_loc(), get_loc_sp_group_ids()
  - Add populate_registry_with_loc() for decentralized peer groups

all_to_all.py:
  - Extract _resolve_group() helper

init_sp.py:
  - Add _parse_loc_config() for loc.enabled/peer_ranks/model_size
  - init_autosp() branches: LOC -> populate_registry_with_loc

loc_sp_bridge.py (NEW):
  - LOCSPShardingAdapter: scatter/gather for SP region
    (mirrors Megatron scatter_to_sequence_parallel_region)
  - LOCRemoteSequentialSPWrapper: wraps BloomBee RemoteSequential
  - LOCSPGradientBridge: DES-LOC Kx-gated gradient sync

sp_compile.py:
  - Consolidate pass_shard_input_ids/label_ids/position_ids into
    unified pass_shard_tagged_inputs with _SHARD_TARGETS table

=== M409: Dispatch loop restructuring ===

autosp_fusion.py:
  - Extract duplicated gather->splice->pad->shard from three VLM
    adapters into reusable _fused_sp_forward() free function
  - Each adapter now only implements _splice_visual_into_text

bloombee_bridge.py:
  - TensorCodec uses _COMPRESS_DISPATCH/_DECOMPRESS_DISPATCH tables
    instead of if/elif chains
  - HeteroSyncGate.should_sync() takes is_last_pass parameter
  - RemoteA2ADoubleBuffer: public selector, alternate_send/recv,
    swap_count tracking

occupancy_grid.py:
  - Extract _compute_blocks_per_sm() helper
  - compute_histogram_grid/filter_grid return full OccupancyResult
  - New compute_dispatch_plan() returns both grids

long_context_checkpointing.py:
  - Convert _CUSTOM_SHOULD_BAN from triple-quoted string to
    parenthesized string concatenation

All files: zero docstrings, zero hash comments.
